name: Astronomy-extension
body:
# Welcome to Astronomy-Extension Pages.
Astronomy-Extension is a SITools2 server's plugin that provides services for astronomy. This page describes the different services and how to set up them in SITools2.

## How to check out this page
you can check out the new branch:
```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```
